ttp_template:
<group name="icmp_seq_ttl_time">
64 bytes from 8.8.8.8: icmp_seq={{ICMP_SEQ}} ttl={{TTL}} time={{TIME | ORPHRASE}} ms
</group>
<group name="rtt_min_rtt_avg_rtt_max_rtt_mdev">
rtt min/avg/max/mdev = {{RTT_MIN}}/{{RTT_AVG}}/{{RTT_MAX}}/{{RTT_MDEV | ORPHRASE}} ms
</group>

textfsm_template:
Value ICMP_SEQ (\d+)
Value TTL (\d+)
Value TIME (\d+\.\d+)
Value TRANSMITTED (\d+)
Value RECEIVED (\d+)
Value LOSS (\d+%)
Value RTT_MIN (\d+\.\d+)
Value RTT_AVG (\d+\.\d+)
Value RTT_MAX (\d+\.\d+)
Value RTT_MDEV (\d+\.\d+)

Start
  ^64 bytes from .+?: icmp_seq=${ICMP_SEQ} ttl=${TTL} time=${TIME} ms$$ -> Record
  ^--- .+ ping statistics ---
  ^${TRANSMITTED} packets transmitted, ${RECEIVED} received, ${LOSS} packet loss, time .+ms$$
  ^rtt min/avg/max/mdev = ${RTT_MIN}/${RTT_AVG}/${RTT_MAX}/${RTT_MDEV} ms$$
